# Technical Spec Writing Rules

## Document Definition
- **Filename**: `outputs/docs/06-개발설계.md`
- **Purpose**: Define architecture, API, data model, integrations, and NFRs
- **Owner**: Engineering Lead

## Prerequisites
- `outputs/docs/04-화면설계.md` approved (can be parallel with 05)

## Strict Sequential Mode (Enforced)

This document is SECTION-GATED. Produce exactly one section per turn and wait for explicit approval before moving on.

### Hard Rules
- Only one section per turn. If asked to "전체 작성", refuse and ask which section to start.
- Use approval phrase to proceed with SECTION TITLE (not numbers).
- Keep process/gate messages in chat, not in the document.

### Per-Section Pre-Work Report (Short)
- Goal: "섹션 N 초안 작성"
- Scope: that section only
- Approach: 2-3 bullets
- Rule Applied: `.cursor/rules/06-개발설계-규칙.mdc`

## Required Sections (Order, One per Turn)
1. 목적 & 범위
2. 전체 아키텍처 개요(클라이언트/백엔드/서드파티)
3. 클라이언트 아키텍처(상태관리/모듈/네비게이션)
4. 백엔드 아키텍처(서비스/DB/캐시) — 해당 시
5. 데이터 모델(엔티티/관계/주요 컬럼)
6. API 명세(엔드포인트/페이로드/응답/상태코드)
7. 오류 처리 & 에러 코드(규약/재시도/타임아웃)
8. 광고 연동(로딩/노출/재로딩/타임아웃/예외)
9. 분석 이벤트(이벤트명/속성/전송 시점)
10. 비기능 요구사항(NFR: 성능/보안/배터리/로깅)
11. 배포 & 릴리스 전략(채널/버전/롤백)
12. 리스크 & 제약

